<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hoodmas || Home</title>
    <style>
        /* all css */
        button {
            margin: 10px 10px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: white;
            background-color: #ff7878;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #ff3b3f;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff3b3f;
            font-family: "Sofia", sans-serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #ababab;
            padding: 10px;                         /* Add some padding around the text */
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        p, .p2{
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }

        /* Snowflake Icon */
        .snowflake {
            font-size: 50px;
            position: fixed;
            top:20px;
            right: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1000;  /* Ensures the snowflake icon stays on top */
            transition: 0.5s;  /* Smooth transition when toggling */
            padding: 10px;
        }

        /* Side Menu */
        .side-menu {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0;  /* Initially hidden */
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: #ff3b3f;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            transition: 0.5s;  /* Smooth transition for opening */
            padding-top: 100px;  /* Space for links */
        }

        /* Side Menu Links */
        .side-menu a {
            padding: 20px 8px 8px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 25px;
            color: white;
            display: block;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* Change color on hover */
        .side-menu a:hover {
            background-color: #ff7878;
            color: black;
        }

        /* Open the side menu */
        .side-menu.open {
            width: 20%;  /* Takes up 20% of the right side */
        }

        .go-back {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50px;
            left: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1000;  
        }

    /* homepage css */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html{
            border-top-style: solid;
            border-top-color:#ff3b3f;
            border-top-width: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;      /* Vertical centering */
            flex-direction: column; 

            margin: auto;
            width: 100px; 
        }

        #hpg-h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 20px 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }



        /* Make the anchor tag fill the container to make the entire image clickable */
        .image-link {
            display: block;
            text-decoration: none;  /* Remove underline from the link */
        }

        /* Container with rounded corners */
        .image-container1, .image-container2, .image-container3 {
            width: 800px;           /* Set the width of the container */
            height: 200px;          /* Set the height of the container */
            border-radius: 20px;    /* Rounded corners */
            overflow: hidden;       /* Ensures the image fits within the container and does not spill over */
            border: 2px solid #ccc; /* Optional: Border around the box */
            position: relative;     /* Needed for responsive layout */
        }

        /* Image inside the container */
        .image-container1 img {
            width: 100%;            /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's width */
            height: 100%;           /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's height */
            object-fit: cover;      /* Ensures the image covers the box without distorting its aspect ratio */
            object-position: 0% 10%;
        }

        /* Image inside the container */
        .image-container2 img {
            width: 100%;            /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's width */
            height: 100%;           /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's height */
            object-fit: cover;      /* Ensures the image covers the box without distorting its aspect ratio */
            object-position: 0% 40%;
        }

        /* Image inside the container */
        .image-container3 img {
            width: 100%;            /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's width */
            height: 100%;           /* Make the image take up 100% of the container's height */
            object-fit: cover;      /* Ensures the image covers the box without distorting its aspect ratio */
            object-position: 0% 45%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        function toggleMenu() {
            var sideMenu = document.getElementById('sideMenu');
            var snowflake = document.querySelector('.snowflake');
            
            // Toggle the 'open' class to show/hide the side menu
            sideMenu.classList.toggle('open');
            
        }
    </script>
    <div class= "homepage">

          <div class="snowflake" onclick="toggleMenu()">
            &#x2744;
          </div>

          <div class="side-menu" id="sideMenu">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/games">Games</a>
            <a href="/secretsanta">Secret Santa</a>
            <a href="/gencorner">Generosity Corner</a>
          </div>


        <div class="go-back"><a href="/logout"><button>Logout</button></a></div>
        <h1>Welcome, <%= users.username %>!</h1>

        <h2 id="hpg-h2">Games</h2>
        <h4>Christmas games are a great way to spread holiday cheer and have fun with friends and family. Inspired from the twelve days of christmas song, here are twelve games for you to choose from!<a href="/games"><button>></button></a></h4>
        <a href="/games" class="image-link">
            <div class="image-container1">
                <img src="goose.webp" alt="Games-link-image1" />
            </div>
        </a>

        <br>
        <br>

        <h2 id="hpg-h2">Secret Santa</h2>
        <h4>Join the fun this holiday season with Secret Santa, where you can create your wishlist and draw another user’s name to fulfill their wishes. It’s a special way to share the joy of giving and receiving thoughtful gifts!<a href="/secretsanta"><button>></button></a></h4>
        <a href="/secretsanta" class="image-link">
            <div class="image-container2">
                <img src="secretsanta.jpg" alt="SS-link-image2" />
            </div>
        </a>

        <br>
        <br>

        <h2 id="hpg-h2">Generosity Corner</h2>
        <h4>Now is your chance to make a meaningful impact, no matter how big or small. Donate clothes, enjoy a warm meal from local restaurants with extra food, or volunteer to support those in need.<a href="/gencorner"><button>></button></a></h4>

        <a href="/gencorner" class="image-link">
            <div class="image-container3">
                <img src="generositycorner.jpg" alt="GC-link-image3" />
            </div>
        </a>

    </div>


</body>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Sofia">
</html>

